# The Interesting Group

A minimalist React website for a small business selling IT products and services, inspired by the style of [GatsbyJS.com](https://www.gatsbyjs.com).

## Features

- Modern, minimalist design with bold typography and gradients
- Animated home page
- Products & Services organized by category
- About Us page
- Contact Us button (links to FormMill)

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repo or extract the ZIP.
2. Run `npm install`
3. Run `npm start`
4. Visit `http://localhost:3000`

## Customization

- Edit `src/pages/Products.jsx` to update products/services.
- Replace the hero image in `src/pages/Home.jsx` with your own.
- Update the contact link in `src/components/Header.jsx` as needed.

